Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.22,0:00:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.23,0:00:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天这儿啊，好像有来过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.63,0:00:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来过几次-是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.17,0:00:43.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是什么类型的都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.51,0:00:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人 OL都可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.38,0:00:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正好午休 -是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.45,0:00:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美丽成熟的年轻的都行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.18,0:01:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一眼看过去人还不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.12,0:01:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上班的年轻女性也不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.00,0:01:11.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能找到几个配合的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.70,0:01:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健身房也是个好地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.04,0:01:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面不都男的吗？ 啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.71,0:02:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真有 -有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.32,0:02:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拍到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.59,0:02:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-边上教练 -那是教练啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.73,0:02:13.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周围人更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.87,0:02:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-真厉害 -是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.90,0:02:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-说是已婚不行 -这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.37,0:03:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-饿了呢 -也走不少路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.98,0:03:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起午饭搞好关系也不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.79,0:03:14.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请客什么  -也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.86,0:03:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有苗头 -这种不太拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:25.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那屁股不错 -不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.67,0:03:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外国人吗 去摸摸看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.94,0:03:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样拍人家吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.41,0:03:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像真是外国人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.95,0:03:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如还是回那吧 恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.54,0:04:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  咦，讨厌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.21,0:04:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.68,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 我没听说有相机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.49,0:04:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会做处理的。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.96,0:05:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 是可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.16,0:05:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是可以简单聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.23,0:05:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一会  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.64,0:05:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我快速点  准备干什么去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.64,0:05:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去买东西 这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.11,0:05:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是什么  能给我们吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.05,0:05:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行   是要自己吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.85,0:05:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送人的  送前辈是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.52,0:05:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送熟人   这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.33,0:05:40.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我刚只是简单说了下想聊聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.74,0:05:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有相机都不用太在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.54,0:05:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不常来这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.55,0:05:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉都是些格调很高的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.75,0:06:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 而且你的服装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.83,0:06:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉和其他人有点不同呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.56,0:06:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是做秘书的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.97,0:06:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.31,0:06:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.91,0:06:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃午饭了吗  还没
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.72,0:06:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也正好饿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.05,0:06:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有推荐饭店吗  推荐吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.52,0:06:39.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话可以边吃边聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.59,0:06:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没这么多可聊的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.27,0:06:50.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近不是都流行拼人交友吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.41,0:06:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是这种感觉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.61,0:07:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简单问问将来规划什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.68,0:07:01.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问这些啊   是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.62,0:07:03.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.08,0:07:08.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相机只是做个记录
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.02,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不太像呀  没有没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.70,0:07:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太拘谨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.83,0:07:20.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就平常心态就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.03,0:07:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用过音源  就可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.91,0:07:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.38,0:07:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有来得及问你名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.92,0:07:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫小慧   恩，小慧小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.65,0:07:42.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冒昧问句  几岁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.86,0:07:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28  恩，28岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.06,0:07:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作时就这样着装吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.13,0:07:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也谈不上是工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.81,0:08:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就随意了   随意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.94,0:08:07.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,服装要求没这么严
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.42,0:08:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常上班也不穿制服吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.22,0:08:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，今天破例穿了私服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.96,0:08:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的工作赚钱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.24,0:08:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月薪大概多少啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.05,0:08:44.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个月都不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.39,0:08:49.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说我总想歪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.86,0:08:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那种多干多得的形式吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.13,0:09:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢，所以我会很努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.54,0:09:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好在意你到底做什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.21,0:09:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才你还提到时间自由散漫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.21,0:09:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊，如果不方便
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.89,0:09:20.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会做消音   真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.69,0:09:25.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是私人好奇想问问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.36,0:09:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这段别用  好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.97,0:09:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个说是工作也。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.04,0:09:42.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是从那些要好的男性那。。。
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.18,0:09:44.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,获取一些金钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.18,0:09:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？从要好男性那得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.72,0:09:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金钱支援吗  是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.26,0:10:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中的爸爸活  是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.87,0:10:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是靠这个生活吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.07,0:10:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那住的地方怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.94,0:10:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住破公寓吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.81,0:10:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种两个半榻榻米大小的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.62,0:10:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给支援的爸爸会出房租
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也借我用用   为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.83,0:10:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有几位  两位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.30,0:10:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有算不上是爸爸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.57,0:10:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共五六个吗  不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.04,0:10:54.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两位爸爸加个会借我钱的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.52,0:11:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说过这个爸爸活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.12,0:11:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会定期付钱，是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.33,0:11:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一次给一大部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.87,0:11:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的手真漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.08,0:11:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太近了啦  太近吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.55,0:11:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也算有好几个情人了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.76,0:11:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是每个人都有肉体关系吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.76,0:11:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦，不啊，都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.37,0:11:50.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有吗，这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.37,0:11:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近什么时候见了  昨天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.78,0:12:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天估计也有吧  恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.05,0:12:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害  基本每天都有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.79,0:12:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺开心的  是有时间表吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.26,0:12:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，会自己做时间规划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.73,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害，真细致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.00,0:12:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是月付吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.47,0:12:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一个月给多少买多久吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.41,0:12:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中两位是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.15,0:12:36.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一位是见面才会给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.08,0:12:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按心情给钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.29,0:12:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等于是日付  恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.09,0:12:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们一样呢  是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:57.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点热了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.24,0:13:02.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过房间里有点热呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.78,0:13:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绿色衣服真棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.78,0:13:13.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很贴身呢 恩，是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.59,0:13:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为需要钱所以玩这个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.93,0:13:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很缺钱吗  不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.80,0:13:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有那么缺钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.00,0:13:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱多点也能买更多东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.27,0:13:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主要是我比较想做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.88,0:13:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各种原因混一起吗  恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.02,0:13:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既能做爱又能拿钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.29,0:13:52.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是一石二鸟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.16,0:13:55.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能吃到想吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.90,0:14:00.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一石三鸟了   是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.97,0:14:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会满足对方性爱要求吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.57,0:14:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像性癖吗  恩  会配合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.78,0:14:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像阿修罗  那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.19,0:14:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像阿修罗那样有多面脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.60,0:14:32.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  第一次被这样评价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.20,0:14:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个人爱怎样玩  个人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.94,0:14:41.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比较喜欢黏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.54,0:14:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位就经常玩婴儿play
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.81,0:14:48.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗，看不出来啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还挺喜欢的  是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.69,0:14:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次出去玩肯定玩这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.02,0:15:02.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息天常玩  是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.36,0:15:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作很劳累  平时又很孤独
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.57,0:15:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以会找点乐子  你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.31,0:15:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得很孤独  是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.51,0:15:23.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很满意现在生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.98,0:15:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有欠缺  比如呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.12,0:15:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我比较爱男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.26,0:15:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以一直在追求邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.53,0:15:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是金钱关系也行？ 恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.68,0:15:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱喝酒吗   恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.02,0:16:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正好有礼物给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.29,0:16:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍等下  我去准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.50,0:16:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合金主兴趣很厉害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.18,0:16:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是一点香槟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.85,0:16:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有比利时啤酒  香槟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.46,0:16:38.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢香槟啊  那就这个吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.46,0:16:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心觉得你好时髦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.87,0:16:52.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰镇过了  谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.74,0:16:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜欢吗  恩 喜欢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.61,0:17:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你的握法很独特呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.95,0:17:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有味道  是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.23,0:17:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点色情  握法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.76,0:17:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚还是摸了摸  有吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.64,0:17:27.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  不自觉做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.57,0:17:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样  我都没有意识到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.38,0:17:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下意识的吧   什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.85,0:17:45.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干什么  等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.86,0:17:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧  你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.93,0:17:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.27,0:18:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是累了吗  也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.61,0:18:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢点  你在干什么啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.75,0:18:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真香
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.49,0:18:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，你这是干什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.25,0:18:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我就感觉不太对劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.77,0:19:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啦，真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.32,0:19:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.46,0:20:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真棒
