Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.69,0:20:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了，你怎么了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.76,0:20:44.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉，什么  真厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.04,0:20:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  就一下 厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.45,0:20:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真色情
