Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.05,0:27:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害啊  很湿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:42.46,0:27:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能看  还没有看到呢
